    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect if you're looking for a solid, well-cared-for car that's ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
