    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips from careful highway commuting. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is clean and smoke-free, with only light softening of the driver\u2019s side bolster to indicate its history. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready, having undergone consistent scheduled maintenance with a recent fluid service and multi-point inspection. It drives tight and true, offering a smooth power delivery that confirms its well-cared-for status. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a dependable, premium experience without the new-car depreciation.",
      "price": 34800.0,
