    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a fantastic ride. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips around town. It drives smoothly, looks great, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that's been well-loved, this is the one for you!",
