    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive rod bearing service utilizing ACL shells and ARP bolts, plus replaced throttle actuators to ensure peak butterfly valve response. The chassis geometry remains sharp, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for variable damping rates. While the aesthetics show minor signs of spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, with a clean subframe and no VANOS irregularities. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for high-revving performance.",
